    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-08-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-08-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="103" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d103">
                <head>No. 103.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-08-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 30,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your cable has been received. I presented your demand promptly. The United
                        States citizens have been already expelled from Nicaragua without; charges
                        or without trial. In spite of my protest Americans marked for arbitrary
                        expulsion. Awaiting your instructions.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
